{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_07_02",
  "title": "鈴村優",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（瑠依を褒めてたら、優が怒るなんて……）\n（俺は、何かマズいことを言ってしまったんだろうか）",
      "startTime": 4.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ゆ、優……！　瑠依の話ばかりして悪かったな\n優の撮影も期待して……",
      "startTime": 11.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 13.1060100556
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "怒ってへんって。何に謝ってはるん？\n期待せんくて結構です",
      "startTime": 17.4393433889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 19.5726776124
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（これは一大事だ！　理由は気になるが）\n（まずは撮影に集中してもらわないと。よし……！）",
      "startTime": 22.5243054435,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6360.655720899998,
          "startTime": 25.9333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8279.999828299999,
          "startTime": 27.8526774407
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 27.6426775933
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 27.9426775933
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……？\n急にうちわなんか持ってきて、何をしてるんです？",
      "startTime": 31.5426775933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "え、炎天下でのグラビア撮影は大変だろう？\n待機中に、少しでも涼んでもらおうと思ってな",
      "startTime": 39.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 42.7956024171
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、少しは涼しくならないか？\nぱたぱたー、ぱたぱたー……",
      "startTime": 46.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "うちわで扇いでもらえるんは、ありがたいけど\n太陽の真下じゃ、ただ熱風をかき回してるだけやん",
      "startTime": 53.0125923049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 57.5148541134
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……そうだ。パラソルの角度も少し調整しよう\nこれで少しは涼しくなったか？",
      "startTime": 62.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "もう……さっきからなんなん",
      "startTime": 64.7325139683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 67.7991821608
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "い、いやぁ、優の調子があまり良くないみたいだから",
      "startTime": 67.7991821608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 72.4711147628
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "うちは、いつもと何も変わりません\n調子が良くないなんてことは、ありません",
      "startTime": 75.4711152715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや……そんなはずは……",
      "startTime": 78.3044480962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、スタッフさんが何か言うてはります",
      "startTime": 80.7544482869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 80.7544482869
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 83.9211149535
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんの撮影、もうちょっとかかるんですね～！\n分かりました、うちはここで待機してます～！",
      "startTime": 88.4877821288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 92.4877816202
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "だ、そうです。すみれちゃんの様子を見に行った方が\nええんやないですか、{user}さん",
      "startTime": 96.1544487955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（やっぱり、俺に対してだけ不機嫌だよな）\n（……どうしたらいいんだ、これは）",
      "startTime": 103.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 106.9463309926
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 106.9463309926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ。やっと、うちの番がきたと思ったのに\n今度は機材トラブルやなんてなぁ",
      "startTime": 112.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "もう少し、このまま待たなあかんみたいですね\n炎天下でじっとしてるんは、辛いわぁ",
      "startTime": 119.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 122.4129900298
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだな。あ！　あっちの売店でアイス売ってるぞ\n冷たいアイスでも食べて、休憩したらどうだ？",
      "startTime": 126.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ついでに怒らせてしまった原因も教えてくれると……",
      "startTime": 129.8415635429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 134.0106506191
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "うちに聞かずにまずは自分の胸に手を当てて\nよーく考えてみたらどうです？",
      "startTime": 137.9439915819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "それに、アイス一つで機嫌が直るなんて\nうち、そんなお子様じゃありません",
      "startTime": 144.7106582485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 147.7106506191
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "うっ、すまん……じゃあ、ええと……そうだ！\n言ってほしい漫画のセリフがあったら、また言うぞ！？",
      "startTime": 153.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 156.8506503902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "そんなん言うて、{user}さん\n声はともかく、演技は全然ダメやったやん",
      "startTime": 159.8173246863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……弁解の余地もございません",
      "startTime": 163.5173170569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 166.1384283545
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ……あははははは\nあかん、もう、我慢出来へん",
      "startTime": 169.8717693172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 172.7384283545
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがそんな落ち込むとは\n思わんかったわ。ほんまごめんなぁ",
      "startTime": 174.9051026506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　ど、どういうことだ？",
      "startTime": 178.2050950212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 181.6444603128
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_07_02-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "今日は大人げない態度をとって\nすみませんでした",
      "startTime": 184.2111346088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
